"1  (3 1/4-pound) boneless pork loin roast, trimmed","1 1/2 teaspoons freshly ground black pepper","1 teaspoon salt","1 teaspoon dry mustard","1 teaspoon dried sage (not rubbed sage)","1/2 teaspoon dried thyme","1 tablespoon olive oil","2 cups sliced onion","1 cup finely chopped leek","1 cup finely chopped carrot","1/2 cup port or other sweet red wine","1/3 cup fat-free, lower-sodium chicken broth","1/3 cup water","1 cup pitted dried plums (about 20 dried plums)","2  bay leaves","2 tablespoons cornstarch","2 tablespoons water"